claim.claim-text:
6. A hand held drill guide for use with a hand held drill motor with a pistol-type grip extending from a main body, said drill guide comprising:
a support arm bracket having a support arm extending therefrom;
a drill motor support bracket including a rear wall attached to said support arm bracket and having first and second spaced resilient limbs configured to receive the drill motor main body thereat, said first and second limbs each including an arcuate limb section, said limb sections contoured toward one another;
a band at said limbs including a tightness varying mechanism;
first and second spaced guide posts connected with said support arm bracket and positioned thereat at opposite sides of said rear wall of said drill motor support bracket;
a ratchet assembly mounted at said support arm bracket, said ratchet assembly including a slotted shaft rotatably maintained through said support arm bracket and having an extended shaft half for ease of insertion thereinto, said shaft and said limbs aligned centrally relative to said spaced guide posts; and
a workpiece engaging strap maintainable around said guide posts and insertable at said slotted shaft of said ratchet assembly.
